<div class="help-content-wrap"><h3 id="how-to-view-transactions-bet-history">How to view transactions &amp; bet history</h3>
<h4 id="how-to-view-my-transactions">How to view my transactions</h4>
<ol>
<li>Log into your account and click on &quot;My Account&quot;.</li>
<li>From the drop-down menu, select the &quot;Transactions&quot; option.</li>
<li>Choose one of 5 transaction categories (Deposits, Withdrawals, Bets, Winnings and Refunds).</li>
<li>Click on the desired tab and the corresponding transaction records will be displayed.</li>
</ol>
<h4 id="how-to-view-my-bet-history">How to view my bet history</h4>
<p>Log into your account and click on &quot;Bet History&quot;.</p>
</div>